                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiachaodongzhi/">冬至</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-04-14</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">充盈着坚毅的信仰，有些句段如此坚毅以至于不像思想而像个人的至高律法</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
